    "correctIndex": 2,
    "explanation": "\\(\\int\\sin^3x\\cos^3x\\,dx=\\int\\sin^3x(1-\\sin^2x)\\cos x\\,dx\\)\n\nLet \\(t=\\sin x\\):\n\n\\(\\int t^3(1-t^2)dt=\\dfrac{t^4}{4}-\\dfrac{t^6}{6}+c=\\dfrac{\\sin^4x}{4}-\\dfrac{\\sin^6x}{6}+c\\)",
