    "correctIndex": 3,
    "explanation": "\\(\\dfrac{\\cos^3x}{\\sin^2x+\\sin x}=\\dfrac{(1-\\sin^2x)\\cos x}{\\sin x(1+\\sin x)}=\\dfrac{(1-\\sin x)\\cos x}{\\sin x}\\)\n\nLet \\(t=\\sin x\\):\n\n\\(\\int\\dfrac{1-t}{t}dt=\\int\\left(\\dfrac{1}{t}-1\\right)dt=\\log|\\sin x|-\\sin x+c\\)",
